<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>HopSearch About Us</title>
<style>
    * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
        font-family: Georgia, "Times New Roman", serif;
        background: #e5e5e5;
        min-height: 100vh;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
    }

   
    .header {
        background: #9fc3a6;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
        padding: 10px 5%;
        width: 100%;
    }

    .logo-container {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 10px;
    }

    .logo-img {
        width: 40px;
        height: 40px;
        object-fit: contain;
    }

    .logo-container span {
        font-size: clamp(18px, 4vw, 24px);
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #333;
    }

    .home {
        font-size: clamp(20px, 4vw, 28px);
        cursor: pointer;
        transition: transform 0.2s;
    }

    .home:hover {
        transform: scale(1.1);
    }

    
    .container {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: stretch;
        padding: 20px;
        max-width: 1400px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        width: 100%;
        flex: 1;
    }

    .side {
        flex: 1 1 250px;
        background: #b9d3b3;
        padding: 30px 20px;
        text-align: center;
        position: relative;
        min-width: 250px;
        margin: 10px;
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }

    .center {
        flex: 2 1 500px;
        background: #d5d9b8;
        text-align: center;
        margin: 10px;
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        min-width: 300px;
    }

   
    h3 {
        font-style: italic;
        font-size: clamp(18px, 3vw, 22px);
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        color: #333;
        border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        padding-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .about-title {
        background: #e6e6e6;
        padding: 15px;
        font-size: clamp(22px, 4vw, 28px);
        font-weight: bold;
        letter-spacing: 2px;
        border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;
    }

    .about-title span {
        color: red;
    }

    .content {
        padding: 25px;
        font-size: clamp(14px, 2vw, 16px);
        line-height: 1.8;
        text-align: justify;
    }

    .side p {
        font-size: clamp(14px, 2vw, 15px);
        line-height: 1.7;
        text-align: justify;
        padding: 0 10px;
    }

    
    .contact {
        background: #e6e6e6;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 25px 20px;
        font-size: clamp(14px, 2vw, 16px);
        font-weight: bold;
        width: 100%;
        margin-top: auto;
        border-top: 3px solid #9fc3a6;
    }

    .contact span {
        color: red;
        font-size: clamp(16px, 2.5vw, 18px);
    }

    .contact-info {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        justify-content: center;
        gap: 20px;
        margin-top: 15px;
    }

    .contact-item {
        background: #9fc3a6;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        border-radius: 25px;
        color: #333;
        font-size: clamp(12px, 1.8vw, 14px);
    }

    
    @media screen and (max-width: 768px) {
        .container {
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 10px;
        }

        .side, .center {
            width: 100%;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }

        .side {
            order: 1;
        }

        .center {
            order: 2;
        }

        .contact-info {
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .contact-item {
            width: 90%;
            max-width: 300px;
        }
    }

    @media screen and (max-width: 480px) {
        .header {
            padding: 8px 15px;
        }

        .logo-img {
            width: 35px;
            height: 35px;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 15px;
        }

        .side {
            padding: 20px 15px;
        }
    }

    
    @media screen and (min-width: 1400px) {
        .container {
            padding: 30px 50px;
        }

        .side {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }
    }

    
    html, body {
        height: 100%;
    }

    body {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
    }

    .container {
        flex: 1 0 auto;
    }

    .contact {
        flex-shrink: 0;
    }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="header">
    <div class="logo-container">
        <img src="hoplog.png" alt="HopSearch Logo" class="logo-img">
        <span>HopSearch</span>
    </div>
    <div class="home"><p></p>Home</div>
</div>

<div class="container">

    <div class="side">
        <h3>MISSION</h3>
        <p>
            To deliver accurate, organized, and accessible healthcare facility
            information through a user-friendly platform that reduces confusion
            and supports efficient decision-making.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="center">
        <div class="about-title">
            ABOUT <span>US</span>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            HopSearch is a centralized web and mobile platform designed to provide
            organized and reliable information about hospitals, clinics, and health
            centers across the Province of Cavite.
            <br><br>
            Recognizing that many healthcare websites present cluttered and unclear data,
            HopSearch was developed to simplify the search process through structured categories,
            service-based filtering, and location-based organization.
            <br><br>
            Our goal is to help users make informed healthcare decisions, especially during urgent situations.
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="side">
        <h3>VISION</h3>
        <p>
            To build a healthcare information system where every user can quickly
            find the most suitable medical facility without uncertainty or delay.
        </p>
    </div>

</div>

<div class="contact">
    <div>CONTACT <span>US</span></div>
    <div class="contact-info">
        <span class="contact-item">SMART - 09793399518</span>
        <span class="contact-item">TEL. NO - (083) 099228</span>
        <span class="contact-item">EMAIL - HOPSEARCH26@GMAIL.COM</span>
    </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
